seo: ActiveMQ,任意文件写入漏洞,CVE-2016-3088,检测,漏洞插件
summary: 该插件用于检测ActiveMQ是否存在CVE-2016-3088任意文件写入漏洞，通过构造特定请求验证漏洞是否存在。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether ActiveMQ has the CVE-2016-3088 arbitrary file write vulnerability by constructing specific requests to verify the existence of the vulnerability.
